race.comment: ELEANOR NANCY (10) has put back-to-back wins together including one over this course and distance last time out. Winning hoop Lloyd stays in the stirrups and is drawn to get all the favours from the inside alley. Goes on top. GREY NORTHERN (8) resumes here but the form she showed when last in work was good enough for a race of this nature. Expect her to be hitting the line with gusto. THEBARBEROFSEVILLE (12) has been plying his trade in harder city outings and should find this assignment much more to his liking. In the mix. TUHINGA (3) is a two-time winner here who gets 2kg weight relief with the claim. Shapes as a key contender. ZHENG YOU (9) next in line despite the sticky draw.
